sText_RoxanneBattleIntro::
# 158 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "I'm so glad to see you again.\n"
	.string "I'm sure we've had many, many\l"
	.string "battles since we've last met.\p"
	.string "I remember first facing you\n"
	.string "not long after you started your\l"
	.string "journey! Now look at\l"
	.string "everything you've achieved.\p"
	.string "Would you kindly demonstrate how\n"
	.string "you battle, and with what POKéMON?$"

sText_RoxanneLastMonSlide::
# 172 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "Oh wow!\n"
	.string "I didn't know you were quite this strong.$"

sText_RoxanneLastMonLowHpSlide::
# 177 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "This has been a great lesson!$"

sText_RoxanneBattlePostWin::
# 181 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "I still have much to learn when it\n"
	.string "comes to battling POKéMON. But\l"
	.string "that only makes me love battling more!$"

sText_RoxanneBattleSpeechPlayerWon::
# 187 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "I learned lots from our battle.$"

sText_RoxanneBattleSpeechPlayerLost::
# 191 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "Back to class with you!$"

sText_DebugBossName_Roxanne::
# 195 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "Roxanne$"

sText_BrawlyPreBattleCall::
# 203 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "BRAWLY is ready to throw down!$"

sText_BrawlyBattleRoomPrompt::
# 207 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "Hey, hurry up!$"

sText_BrawlyBattleIntro::
# 211 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "I haven't seen you in a while,\n"
	.string "{PLAYER}!\p"
	.string "Where have I been? Well,\n"
	.string "I've travelled the seas of HOENN\l"
	.string "and beyond.\p"
	.string "I've learned first hand how\n"
	.string "you need to be tough to survive\l"
	.string "in this world.\p"
	.string "Do you have what it takes to\n"
	.string "beat me this time?\p"
	.string "I'd like to see you try!$"

sText_BrawlyLastMonSlide::
# 229 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
	.string "Come on, {B_OPPONENT_MON1_NAME}!\n"
	.string "Lend me your strength.$"

sText_BrawlyLastMonLowHpSlide::
# 234 "data/text/factory_boss_texts.pory"
